<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>ZPanel: New Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello, {{name}}!</h1>
    <p>You have received a new notification on the ZPanel platform.</p>
    <p><b>Title:</b> {{title}}</p>
    <p><b>Message:</b> {{{message}}}</p>
    <br/>
    <p>To view more details or take action, please click the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="{{url}}">View Notification</a></p>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
    <p>Thank you for using ZPanel!</p>
</body>
</html>